                <div class="entry-c">
                    <div class="entry-title">
                        <h2><a href="#">OMINIRA (LIBERTAD)</a></h2>
                    </div>
                    <ul class="entry-meta clearfix">
                        <li><a href="#"><i class="icon-time"></i> 11:00 - 19:00</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#"><i class="icon-map-marker2"></i> Perth</a></li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="entry-content">
                        <p>En su jaula virtual dos hombres intentas inútilmente entonar su canto de vida.&nbsp;<span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:1,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:270}">&nbsp;</span></p>
                        <p>Después de un largo éxodo recuperan su libertad… pero&nbsp;continúan&nbsp;unidos, no&nbsp;conciben la vida con independencia física y espiritual. Les&nbsp;ahogaron&nbsp;los&nbsp;caminos, cegaron sus voces y enmudecieron sus ojos, temen volar.&nbsp;<span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:1,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:270}">&nbsp;</span></p>
                        <p>Un día rompen las rejas, tienden las alas de palabras y vuelan.&nbsp;<span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:1,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:270}">&nbsp;</span></p>
                        <p>Recuperan su cultura, su identidad, su civilización, su vida, su&nbsp;ominira&nbsp;…<span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:1,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:270}">&nbsp;</span></p>
                        <p>Una obra de danza afro moderna creada y dirigida por Gaby&nbsp;Fabro&nbsp;montada&nbsp;sobre una&nbsp;rica variedad musical de temas afrocubanos, tangos y&nbsp;música&nbsp;instrumental, con poesía de Rogelio Martínez&nbsp;Furé&nbsp;(poeta cubano).&nbsp;<span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:1,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:270}">&nbsp;</span></p>
                        <p>2015&nbsp;<span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:1,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:270}">&nbsp;</span></p>
                        <p>Abril–Mayo, Teatro El Popular (CABA)&nbsp;<span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:1,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:270}">&nbsp;</span></p>
                        <p>2016&nbsp;<span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:1,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:270}">&nbsp;</span></p>
                        <p>Junio&nbsp;– Teatro Margarita Xirgu (Espacio UNTREF), en el&nbsp;marco del&nbsp;Festival Solidario Vengo a ofrecer mi corazón,&nbsp;apoyando&nbsp;al pueblo&nbsp;ecuatoriano.&nbsp;<span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:1,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:270}">&nbsp;</span></p>
                        <p>Julio–&nbsp;Teatro York (OLIVOS)&nbsp;<span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:1,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:270}">&nbsp;</span></p>
                        <p>Agosto – Teatro&nbsp;Martí&nbsp;de Santiago de Cuba, en el marco de&nbsp;la celebración del&nbsp;homenaje al ya desaparecido Maestro Eduardo Rivero y al Maestro Ramiro&nbsp;Guerra, considerado el padre de la danza cubana.&nbsp;<span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:1,&quot;335551550&quot;:1,&quot;335551620&quot;:1,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:270}">&nbsp;</span></p>
                        <p><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}">&nbsp;</span></p>
                    </div>
